| What it is               | A contract for how any two pieces of         | A specific standard for how an AI model talks        |
|                          | software talk to each other                  | to tools/data sources                                |
+--------------------------+----------------------------------------------+------------------------------------------------------+
| Who defines the format   | Each API has its own request/response        | One consistent format — the AI just discovers        |
